## Практический пример

```python
commands = {
    "hello": lambda: print("hi"),
    "exit": lambda: exit()
}

while True:
    cmd = input(">> ").strip()

    if cmd in commands:
        commands[cmd]()
    else:
        print("unknown command")
```

